<h2>Add Role</h2>
<p>
The page allows you to add roles.
</p>

## Call the global marcro to show errors for the form
#showAllFieldErrors ($form)

<form method="post" action="$link.setAction('security.AddRole').setPage('security,Roles.vm')">
  #set ($rolename = $form.Fields.get("rolename"))
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Add Role</legend>
    <label for="groupname">Role Name: </label>
    <input type="text" size="10" name="rolename" value="$rolename.Value" />
    <br />    
	<input type="submit" value="Add Role" />
  </fieldset>
</form>

